name: prayer to Holy Guardian Angel
description:
magick sigil, visual mantra of connection with the Holy Guardian Angel. 
this work is a tattoo art, animated in gif, as an iconographic suggestion to enhance a specific intent to increase ties with the HGA and manifest its potential. 
it is part of a magick study of a series of sigils produced over my years of practice. 
this work also has the potential to be programmed as a servitor according to the user's will
